{"tid":1771340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬料水水警基地 水警快艇沉沒","createTime":"2019-12-05T22:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T23:49:05.000Z","uid":6497,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"50646cadad99af03dc1071e59a16e7015ae80f2a","tid":1771340,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T22:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191206/large/1575582580_a89a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191206%2Flarge%2F1575582580_a89a.jpg&h=0257c4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191206/large/1575582018_a027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191206%2Flarge%2F1575582018_a027.jpg&h=c74e7216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬料水水警北分區基地發生沉船事故，凌晨4時，一艘泊於岸邊約10米長水警快艇，疑入水沉沒，事件中無人受傷。警方在場拉起封鎖線，調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生時，天文台發出強烈季候風信號，預料本港吹偏北強風，平均風速每小時超過40公里，陣風間中達烈風程度。大埔風浪頗大，未知意外是否與強風有關。"},{"pid":"0b2e6b9ece57d4e5763829cf7ef3bcf777aa6d2c","tid":1771340,"uid":247613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T22:05:59.000Z","msg":"Jeng"},{"pid":"b50c7266d4b75f4f886193093ac38429f7bca263","tid":1771340,"uid":212336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T22:06:57.000Z","msg":"事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n咁把撚咩"},{"pid":"f26960b8bf430930896a1f1e7cdc00ce003ae427","tid":1771340,"uid":56999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T22:08:10.000Z","msg":"事件中無人受傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5212a32cbb435db05c8aa9745e3f6a0ed7050fb","tid":1771340,"uid":232660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T22:11:01.000Z","msg":"喜歡你讓我下沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3e0873e3dc30bc71fb75f1ead5a59c0c62ed7b"